text:
When I came to Congress, I promised to work with anyone who would do right by Upstate New York.

My Lowering Egg Prices Act will put millions of American eggs back on the market and lower grocery bills.

@SecRollins, I look forward to working together to get this bill passed. https://t.co/0NaDNOGEdf

The Local Food Purchase Assistance Program is a lifeline for our farmers and food banks. 

After a few long days of gridlock, I was proud to lead this bipartisan moment to help our neighbors who need it most. 

@HouseAgGOP, let's get it done. https://t.co/eWaZQ2uIlP
